General.Name: Bawat Water Technologies AB
General.Description: Bawat Water Technologies AB, through its subsidiary, focuses on the provision of heat-based water treatment technologies. The company provides heat-based ballast water management system, a solution for ballast water treatment in ports, terminals, and shipyards, as well as for jack-up rigs, offshore construction vessels (OCV)/platform supply vessels (PSV), ports based solution, barges, semi-submersibles, and drillships. Bawat Water Technologies AB was founded in 2011 and is headquartered in Horsholm, Denmark.
